Recommends: aptura-apps
Description: Aptura OS default system metapackage
 Top-level dependency package that pulls in the complete default Aptura OS
 install: branding, the Aptura Shell desktop, system policy defaults, the
 everyday application set, and the Aptura custom kernel.
 .
 Editing this package's dependencies is how the default install evolves.
